#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.174"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.174:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.174:0.2"
msgid "18. Sañcetaniyavagga "
msgstr "18. Intention "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.174:0.3"
msgid "174. Ānandasutta "
msgstr "174. With Ānanda "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.174:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā ānando yenāyasmā mahākoṭṭhiko tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā mahākoṭṭhikena saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then Venerable Ānanda went up to Venerable Mahākoṭṭhita, and exchanged greetings with him. "

msgctxt "an4.174:1.2"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ mahākoṭṭhikaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, Ānanda sat down to one side, and said to Mahākoṭṭhita: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.174:2.1"
msgid "“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī”ti? "
msgstr "“Reverend, when these six fields of contact have faded away and ceased with nothing left over, does anything else exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.174:3.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an4.174:4.1"
msgid "“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī”ti? "
msgstr "“Does nothing else exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.174:5.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.174:6.1"
msgid "“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ kiñcī”ti? "
msgstr "“Do both something else and nothing else exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc7
msgctxt "an4.174:7.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.174:8.1"
msgid "“Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ kiñcī”ti? "
msgstr "“Do neither something else nor nothing else exist?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc9
msgctxt "an4.174:9.1"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, āvuso”. "
msgstr "“Don’t put it like that, reverend.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc10
msgctxt "an4.174:10.1"
msgid "“‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr "“Reverend, when asked these questions, "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.2"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr "you say ‘don’t put it like that’. "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.3"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.4"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.5"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.6"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.7"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti puṭṭho samāno: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.8"
msgid "‘mā hevaṃ, āvuso’ti vadesi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an4.174:10.9"
msgid "Yathā kathaṃ panāvuso, imassa bhāsitassa attho daṭṭhabbo”ti? "
msgstr "… How then should we see the meaning of this statement?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.163, sc11
msgctxt "an4.174:11.1"
msgid "“‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti. "
msgstr "“If you say that ‘when the six fields of contact have faded away and ceased with nothing left over, something else exists’, you’re proliferating the unproliferated. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.2"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti. "
msgstr "If you say that ‘nothing else exists’, you’re proliferating the unproliferated. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.3"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā atthi ca natthi ca aññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti. "
msgstr "If you say that ‘both something else and nothing else exist’, you’re proliferating the unproliferated. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.4"
msgid "‘Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā nevatthi no natthaññaṃ kiñcī’ti, iti vadaṃ appapañcaṃ papañceti. "
msgstr "If you say that ‘neither something else nor nothing else exist’, you’re proliferating the unproliferated. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.5"
msgid "Yāvatā, āvuso, channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ gati tāvatā papañcassa gati. "
msgstr "The scope of the six fields of contact extends as far as the scope of proliferation. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.6"
msgid "Yāvatā papañcassa gati tāvatā channaṃ phassāyatanānaṃ gati. "
msgstr "The scope of proliferation extends as far as the scope of the six fields of contact. "

msgctxt "an4.174:11.7"
msgid "Channaṃ, āvuso, phassāyatanānaṃ asesavirāganirodhā papañcanirodho papañcavūpasamo”ti. "
msgstr "When the six fields of contact fade away and cease with nothing left over, proliferation stops and is stilled.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.174:11.8"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

